author: Mih
text: This is so lovely and sad at the same time. Brazilians love bossa nova but no one creates it anymore, it takes people from other countries to create masterpieces so we can relive my childhood feelings of listening to a fresh bossa nova - piada nao intencional. The best is that it sounds so much like the most famous ones and not the elevator music everyone associates it with 🙄, completely fills my heart. So tank you so much laufey for pouring all your talent into this underappreciated genre, do know we appreciate you a LOT ♥
